(b) A violation of this section is a Class C misdemeanor, punishable only by the
completion of a court-approved handgun safety course. The court shall not impose a
fine or incarceration as punishment for a violation of this section.
SECTION 4. This act takes effect July 1, 2025, the public welfare requiring it.
